      "value": {
        "latex": "Soit $A$ un anneau commutatif et $I$ un id{\\'e}al de $A$.\n\nOn note $\\sqrt{I} = \\{ x \\in A \\text{ tq } \\exists\\ n \\in \\N \\text{ tq } x^n \\in I \\}$\n(radical de $I$).",
        "html": "<p>Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\(A\\)</span> un anneau commutatif et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(I\\)</span> un id<span>é</span>al de <span class=\"math inline\">\\(A\\)</span>.</p>\n<p>On note <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\sqrt{I} = \\{ x \\in A \\text{ tq } \\exists\\ n \\in \\N \\text{ tq } x^n \\in I \\}\\)</span> (radical de <span class=\"math inline\">\\(I\\)</span>).</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "cd829f1b-b624-4355-8cd5-7bbb4046cb1b",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Montrer que $\\sqrt{I}$ est un id{\\'e}al de $A$.",
        "html": "<p>Montrer que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\sqrt{I}\\)</span> est un id<span>é</span>al de <span class=\"math inline\">\\(A\\)</span>.</p>\n"
